== Umwuga ==
Mu 1998 yakoze umwanya wa mbere 'Vusi Moletsane' muri isabune izwi cyane ''Isidingo'' yamenyekanye cyane. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-03-26-meshack-mavuso-on-being-broke-id-go-to-the-bathroom--cry/</ref> Hanyuma, yagaragaye mu ikinamico ''Yizo Yizo'' yerekanwe kuva 1999 kugeza 2004 afite uruhare 'Jabulani "Javas" Nyembe'. <ref>https://www.power987.co.za/featured/listen-yizo-yizo-made-meshack-mavusos-acting-career/</ref>

Yamenyekanye kandi ubwo yinjiraga muri Mzansi Magic telenovela Isithembiso yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 3 Mata 2017, aho yakinnye imico ya Keromemang Mtimande, se wa Tshepo, wabitswe na se na nyina kugeza igihe yavumbuwe mu buryo butangaje. gira umwana numukunzi we Chlodea ubu bakundana numwanzi we.

Yatangiye umwuga we nka Meshack Mavuso akina 'Simiso Mtshali' mu gihembwe cya kabiri n'icya gatatu cy'urukurikirane rw'abapolisi ''Zero Tolerance'' rwerekanwe muri SABC2. Mbere yizo nshingano zashimiwe, yakinnye imico itandukanye itemewe muri saison yambere. Mu mwaka wa 2008, yari umwe mu babyinnyi b'ibyamamare mu Kubyina umwaka mushya udasanzwe ''uza'', byacishijwe ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2008. <ref name="tvsa">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=3100 "Mavuso Magabane"]. ''tvsa''. 2020-11-26<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2020-11-26</span></span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2009, yagaragaye ashyigikiwe nigihembwe cyambere cyuruhererekane rwerekana ibisekuruza ''Who Do You Think You Are?'' cyari gishingiye ku ruhererekane rw'Abongereza rw'izina rimwe. Urukurikirane rwaciwe kuri SABC2 muri 2009. Muri 2014, yagarutse kuri tereviziyo akina abashyitsi mu bice bibiri by'ikinamico ya Sida ''City'' yakinnye nka 'dogiteri'. Muri 2015, ku nshuro ya mbere, yakoresheje izina Mavuso Magabane kuri televiziyo ''Zabalaza'' . Muri serial, yakinnye abashyitsi mugice kimwe. Muri 2016 yakoze umwanya wa kabiri ayoboye muri e.tv ikinamico ''yubujura Heist'' hamwe ninshingano ya 'Chairman'. 

Muri 2020 nyuma yigihe gito muri serial ''The River'', yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba serial ''Durban Gen'' aho akina imico ya Dr Thabo Dlamini ugaragara nkumugore kandi akaba yarashakanye na Dr Precious Dlamini. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/meshack-mavuso-on-starring-in-durban-gen-and-lessons-hes-learnt-in-his-career-20200930</ref>

